title: Style.Stitch.Staple.Basic.Upholstering.Skills.to.Tackle.Any.Proj
description:
Format: EPub
Genre: Upholstering/tutorial
Published: 2013

Book Description: Style, Stitch, Staple combines straightforward upholstery techniques with advice on choosing and styling fabrics to help the design-savvy reader transform even the most dilapidated furniture into gorgeous updated pieces. Packed full of fabric advice, yardage charts, upholstery tutorials, and case studies that feature salvaged and inexpensive furniture, this book is the perfect go-to-guide for the many sewers, designers, artists, and creative folk who want to learn to rescue and revive all manner of furniture-footstools, headboards, or dining room chairs-to give their homes that unique, personalized, and stylish look
